{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-discuss-your-morning-or-evening-routine/task-27","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-discuss-your-morning-or-evening-routine","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Neno <span class=\"highlighted-text\">never</span> je prilog koji se koristi za označavanje \"nikad\" ili \"u bilo kojem trenutku\". Često se koristi kada se govori o stvarima koje osoba ne radi ili nikada nije uradila. Primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">I have never been to Australia.</span> - To znači da ta osoba nikada nije posetila Australiju u bilo kojem trenutku.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">She never eats fast food.</span> - Ovo znači da nije jeo brzi obrok u bilo kojem trenutku.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Reč <span class=\"highlighted-text\">thought</span> je prošlo vreme od <span class=\"highlighted-text\">think</span>. <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Thought of that</span> znači da je razmislio ili došao do ideje ranije. Na primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">I thought of going to the beach, but it was too cold.</span> - To znači da je ta osoba razmišljala o odlasku na obalu.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-discuss-your-morning-or-evening-routine/task-27"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>James šta znači kada kaže <span class=\"highlighted-text\">I had never thought of that</span>?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Nikad nije razmišljao/razmišljala o toj ideji ranije.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Često razmišlja o tome</p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Never</span> ukazuje na odsustvo akcije ili ideje, pa to znači da nikada nije razmišljao/mislio o tome, a ne da misli često.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Uvek izbegava da razmišlja o tome</p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Never thought of that</span> to znači da nikada nije razmišljao, ne mora da se izbegava namerno.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Često razmišlja o tome</p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Never</span> to ukazuje da se nikada nije dogodilo, pa nije o učestalnim mislima.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":1}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-breakroom.png","characters":[{"character":"James","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.2},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"2.2-1.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":48.56,"finishTimestamp":52.1},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"James","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"James","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":4.54,"dialogue":{"text":"An early coffee and then breakfast. I had never thought of that.","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"James","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":5.04,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 27","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/#learn-how-to-discuss-your-morning-or-evening-routine","dashedName":"task-27","certification":"a2-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-how-to-discuss-your-morning-or-evening-routine","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-discuss-your-morning-or-evening-routine/task-28","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-h